dublin_core.dcvalue: Sailesh Chutani, CEO/Co-Founder, MobiSante, Email: sailesh.chutani@mobisante.com

A mobile diagnostic system that allows health professionals to conduct ultrasound assessment at the point of care. MobiUS uses a smartphone (or tablet), transducer probe and software that enables providers to perform routine screenings, and diagnostic imaging.
